<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ وج:</span> رَجُلٌ <span class="c2">(أَهْوَجُ)</span> بَيِّنُ <span class="c2">(الْهَوَجِ)</span> بِفَتْحَتَيْنِ أَيْ طَوِيلٌ وَفِيهِ تَسَرُّعٌ وَحُمْقٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>